trans-unit.source: Azure API Management REST API Backend entity
trans-unit.target: Azure API Management REST API Backend entity

trans-unit.source: The Backend entity in <token>azure_apimgt_3</token> represents a backend service that hosts the APIs called by API Management applications.
trans-unit.target: The Backend entity in <token>azure_apimgt_3</token> represents a backend service that hosts the APIs called by API Management applications.
